1. *Mali* ljudi su uglavnom ljubazni. (Small people are usually friendly.)
2. Ona ima *malu* kuću u selu. (She has a small house in the village.)
3. On je *malo* usamljen. (He is a bit lonely.)
4. Naš mali grad je prelep. (Our small town is beautiful.)
5. *Malog* deteta su uvek zabavljali. (They always entertained the little child.)
6. On je bio *mali* kad je došao u školu. (He was small when he came to school.)
7. Učenici su bili *mali* i prestrašeni. (The students were small and scared.)
8. *Malim* ždrebicima je potrebna mnogo pažnje. (Little chicks need a lot of attention.)